---
title: Honey Chipotle Salmon & Halloumi with Slaw & Rainbow Veggie Fries
description: Sweet, smokey, and perfectly flaky - tonight’s blushing pink salmon is a real showstopper. The sweet chipotle glaze is a perfect match for this tender fish, and paired with a crunchy, refreshing slaw and colourful rainbow veggie fries, this dish brings a healthy twist to bold flavours.
